  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, whisk together chili sauce, garlic, ginger, and 1 tablespoon olive oil.",
    "3. Add cooked lentils to the bowl and toss to combine.",
    "4. Thread red onion, bell pepper, and lemongrass onto skewers.",
    "5. Brush skewers with remaining 2 tablespoons olive oil.",
    "6. Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally.",
    "7. Serve grilled skewers hot with lentil mixture spooned over the top."
